==English==
===Noun===
Generica. Abbreviation of "Generic America". Describes features such as Fire Hydrants, Letter Boxes, McDonalds, KFC, Wendy's, Streets called "Main" that are the same wherever you go.
===Quotes===
“We were so lost in generica, I actually forgot what city we were in” -- John Perry Barlow
